lead_paragraph: We publish on our outside the news received by the Empire City. including a list of the rcmainder of the " Liberators" sent to Spain, as well as of those in the hospital at Havana, an interesting circular from Mr. J. S. THRASHER to the friends of the transported, a farewell letter of the prisoners, and other valuable items of intelligence.
